bootsetup (1.1.1)

  * Added Wi-Fi config script for NetworkManager
  * Added WireGuard config script
  * Added nftables config script
  * Added config scripts which can be run every time
  * Changed locking mechanism
  * *bootfs* partition default path was changed to `/boot/firmware` mount (according to RPi)
  * Added *network-online.target* as requirement for executing init scripts (so nmcli can be used)

 -- Martin Dagarin <martin.dagarin@gmail.com>  2025-02-05

